data.description: Located in Cypress Trace, this beautiful townhouse is perfect place to call home. Driving into Cypress Trace, you'll pass a serene lake which can be seen from the back common area & deck. 2 bedrooms 2 baths with a loft overlooking the living room. The home features laminate flooring and upgraded soft carpet. Custom cabinetry was installed underneath the bar area for more storage. Counters have been redone recently as well as painting of cabinets to update kitchen. New hardware and a new backsplash has been recently installed to complete the look! This home also has new paint throughout the home!  There is a nice back deck that is large enough for a sitting area. Back deck also has a large bench installed along the rail and has additional locked storage room on deck.
